<meta name="DCTERMS.bibliographicCitation" content="Destrade, M., Du, Y., Blackwell, J., Colgan, N., &amp; Balbi, V. (2023). Canceling the elastic Poynting effect with geometry. Physical Review E, 107(5), L053001. doi: 10.1103/PhysRevE.107.L053001" xml:lang="en_IE" />
